        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Objection one: It would seem that the appetite is not a special power of the soul.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "For no power of the soul is to be assigned for those things which are common to animate and to inanimate things.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Therefore the appetite is not a special power of the soul.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "But each power of the soul desires some particular desirable thing-namely its own suitable object.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "To make this evident, we must observe that some inclination follows every form: for example, fire, by its form, is inclined to rise, and to generate its like.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Now, the form is found to have a more perfect existence in those things which participate knowledge than in those which lack knowledge.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Therefore this natural form is followed by a natural inclination, which is called the natural appetite.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000014_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000014_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Therefore, as forms exist in those things that have knowledge in a higher manner and above the manner of natural forms; so must there be in them an inclination surpassing the natural inclination, which is called the natural appetite.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Therefore it is necessary to assign to the soul a particular power.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Now, it is diversity of aspect in the objects, and not material diversity, which demands a diversity of powers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Wherefore each power desires by the natural appetite that object which is suitable to itself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Whether the Sensitive and Intellectual Appetites Are Distinct Powers?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000020_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Objection one: It would seem that the sensitive and intellectual appetites are not distinct powers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000020_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000020_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "But it is accidental to the appetible object whether it be apprehended by the sense or by the intellect.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000020_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000020_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Therefore the sensitive and intellectual appetites are not distinct powers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Therefore the intellectual appetite is not distinguished from the sensitive.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "But the motive power which in man follows the intellect is not distinct from the motive power which in animals follows sense.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Wherefore differences in the thing apprehended are of themselves differences of the appetible.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_245693_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/245693/7326_245693_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Wherefore the Philosopher says (Rhetoric.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "One of Judge Methuen's pet theories is that the soul in the human body lies near the center of gravity; this is, I believe, one of the tenets of the Buddhist faith, and for a long time I eschewed it as one might shun a vile thing, for I feared lest I should become identified even remotely with any faith or sect other than Congregationalism.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "I mentioned this circumstance to Judge Methuen, and it seemed to please him.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000004_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000004_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "What you have just told me convinces me that you are by nature qualified for rare exploits in the science and art of book collecting.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "It occurred to the Judge long ago to prepare a list of the names of the famous bald men in the history of human society, and this list has grown until it includes the names of thousands, representing every profession and vocation.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Kings should serve the honorable purpose of indicating to humanity that bald heads are favored with the approval and the protection of Divinity.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "In my own case I have imputed my early baldness to growth in intellectuality and spirituality induced by my fondness for and devotion to books.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Miss Susan, my sister, lays it to other causes, first among which she declares to be my unnatural practice of reading in bed, and the second my habit of eating welsh rarebits late of nights.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000009_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000009_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Over my bed I have a gas jet so properly shaded that the rays of light are concentrated and reflected downward upon the volume which I am reading.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Miss Susan insists that much of this light and its attendant heat falls upon my head, compelling there a dryness of the scalp whereby the follicles have been deprived of their natural nourishment and have consequently died.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "She furthermore maintains that the welsh rarebits of which I partake invariably at the eleventh hour every night breed poisonous vapors and subtle megrims within my stomach, which humors, rising by their natural courses to my brain, do therein produce a fever that from within burneth up the fluids necessary to a healthy condition of the capillary growth upon the super adjacent and exterior cranial integument.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "And indeed baldness has its compensations; when I look about me and see the time, the energy, and the money that are continually expended upon the nurture and tending of the hair, I am thankful that my lot is what it is.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "For now my money is applied to the buying of books, and my time and energy are devoted to the reading of them.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Let me paraphrase my dear Chaucer and tell thee, thou waster of substances, that",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-7326_96553_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/7326/96553/7326_96553_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-7326",
        "content": "Books, books, books-give me ever more books, for they are the caskets wherein we find the immortal expressions of humanity-words, the only things that live forever!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very low"
